{"article_id":"vnDqpVHYehX4oOFW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump said Wednesday night","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"he ' s prepared to walk away from the bargaining table at an historic summit with Kim Jong-un","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"if he feels","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"the North Korean leader isn ' t negotiating in good faith over giving up his nuclear weapons .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"\" If","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"I think","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"it ' s a meeting","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that is not going to be fruitful ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"we ' re not going to go , \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Trump said at a press conference with Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"\" If the meeting ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"when I ' m there ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"is not fruitful ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"I will respectfully leave the meeting . \"","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"The president plans to meet with Mr. Kim in late May or early June","depth":3},{"id":15,"text":"to discuss denuclearization of the communist nation ,","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"which has also been testing intercontinental ballistic missiles and raising its threats against the U.S. and its allies .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Trump revealed Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that he dispatched CIA Director Mike Pompeo earlier this month","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to meet with Mr. Kim in Pyongyang","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to lay the groundwork for a summit between the two leaders .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The president said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that meeting went \" very smoothly . \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" We have come a long way with North Korea , \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"\" We ' ve never been in a position like this with that regime . \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Previous U.S. administrations have failed to persuade North Korea to stop developing nuclear weapons ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"with Pyongyang backing out of promised concessions","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"after obtaining shipments of food or other humanitarian aid from the U.S.","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"he ' s well aware of North Korea ' s reputation","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"of bargaining in bad faith .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"we \" re going to be successful , \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" But ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"if for any reason I feel","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"we ' re not ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"we end . \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Mr. Abe ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"who is pressing Mr. Trump to raise the issue of North Korea ' s abductions of Japanese citizens ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"he ' s hopeful","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"the summit will be successful .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"\" We strongly hope for a breakthrough , \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Mr. Abe said through a translator .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" There could be a path","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to settle the unfortunate past . \"","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Three U.S. citizens are still being held by North Korea","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"- Kim Sang-duk and Kim Hak-song ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"who have been held more than a year ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and Kim Dong-chul ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"who was detained in 2015 for unknown reasons .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"The president said","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"the U.S. is \" negotiating now \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"to gain their release .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"\" They do have three prisoners , \"","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"\" We have been talking about them .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"It ' s harsh treatment .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"We ' re having a very good dialogue .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"there ' s a good chance . \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"The president said","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"he wants North Korea to abandon its nuclear-weapons program in a \" complete and verifiable and irreversible way . \"","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"A plan","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"being floated among Japan , the U.S. and South Korea","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"is aimed at the complete denuclearization of North Korea by the summer of 2020 ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"diplomatic sources say ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"while Pyongyang is pursuing a phased approach in exchange for benefits .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"In another potential breakthrough , Mr. Kim will hold a summit next week with South Korean President Moon Jae-in .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"The two sides are pursing a formal peace treaty","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"to end the war","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that began in 1950 .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Mr. Trump has been saying","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"the U.S. has no choice","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"but to try to reach a deal with nuclear-armed Pyongyang after years of failure and hostilities .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"\" We hope to see the day","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"when the whole Korean peninsula can live together in safety , prosperity and peace , \"","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" We hope","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"it all works out ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"we ' ll be trying very hard . \"","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"The president thanked Mr. Abe for working with the U.S.","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"to keep economic and diplomatic pressure on Pyongyang","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to come to the negotiating table .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"\" Our campaign of maximum pressure will continue","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"until North Korea denuclearizes .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"We have to end nuclear weapons ideally in all parts of the world , \"","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":103,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":93,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":0,"right":92,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":92,"left":1,"right":91,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":98,"right":101,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":96,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":8,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":5,"right":94,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":13,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":105,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":14,"right":104,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":126,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":113,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":108,"right":112,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":17,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":18,"right":106,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"purpose"